---
title: Lemon Parsley Chicken Paillard with Balsamic Burrata, Arugula Salad & Toasted Bread
description: In tonight's dinner, chicken cutlets are pounded extra-thin, cooked in a buttery blend of lemon and parsley, then drizzled in tangy balsamic glaze. On the side, there’s toasty bread and an arugula salad with balsamic tomatoes and burrata mozzarella. Simple, quick, and elegant—you’ll have perfectly cooked paillard in no time flat!
